query: What is the net income per FTE in 2024 at Apple?
output:
The Form 10‑K states Apple had approximately 164,000 full‑time equivalent employees as of September 28, 2024 (Part I, “Human Capital”). Apple’s consolidated net income for fiscal 2024 was $93,736 million (Consolidated Statements of Operations).

Net income per full‑time equivalent (FTE) = Net income / FTEs
= $93,736 million / 164,000 FTEs
= $571,365 per FTE (approximately)

So Apple’s 2024 net income per full‑time equivalent was about $571,000.
